text: I met with the <http://Keen.io|Keen.io> folks last week in SF. They provide integration of various analtytics tools. They've been doing some work in the IOT space as well: <https://keen.io/blog/86348350211/how-pebble-uses-keen-io-for-analytics>

attachments.title: Keen IO - Analytics for Developers
attachments.text: Keen IO is a set of powerful APIs that allow you to collect, analyze, and visualize events from anything connected to the internet.
